hifiberry-pipewire (1.4.5.3) stable; urgency=low

  * Updated build script to use changelog as single source of truth for versioning
  * Improved version consistency and management
  * Added hifiberry-pipewire.service file for debhelper-compatible systemd integration
  * Enhanced postinst script with idempotent user/group creation and upgrade detection
  * Improved systemd service management following Debian best practices
  * Added pipewire group membership for better audio device access control
  * Added fix-pipewire-config script to disable problematic D-Bus modules for headless systems
  * Fixed PipeWire startup errors in headless environments by disabling portal, jackdbus-detect, and x11-bell modules
  * Implemented proper configuration file management with .default template approach
  * Added automatic backup of customized configurations during package removal
  * Improved configuration preservation and restoration during upgrades
  * Created /etc/pipewire/pipewire.conf.d/ directory for configuration overrides
  * Optimized build configuration to exclude debug symbols for smaller package size
  * Added explicit symbol stripping and NDEBUG flag for release builds

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Tue, 02 Jul 2025 12:00:00 +0000

